Minimizing $\phi$ with respect to $\eta$ and $P$ yields the equations of state:
\begin{eqnarray}
\eta(\alpha + \beta \eta^2 + \gamma \eta^4 + \delta P^2) & = & 0 \label{eq:eos1}\\
P(1+\delta\chi_0\eta^2) & = & \chi_0 E \label{eq:eos2}
\end{eqnarray}

